<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Gabriel Ridler, Bürger zu München</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er gemäß dem Bittbrief der Herzöge Ernst I. und Wilhelm III. von Bayern-München Anton Ridler in das Bürgerrecht aufnimmt; dies gilt nur bis zum Jakobstag und bei Anwesenheit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="64r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l2">Gabriel Ridler <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü München </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l3">Lıeber her Rıdler / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Anthoni <expan>Rıdl<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l4"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> Suns <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ernſts vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> VVılhalms </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l5">briefs 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ab </del> ein abſchrift / vnd auch iren betbrief an vns damit geſant habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l6">das alles <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Nu ıſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat gewonheit nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l9">daʒ vvir yemanden cʒü <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_line_1576576424103_2551">bey vns </ab></add> empfahen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_line_1576576427322_2556">oder purkrecht verſprechen </ab></add> er ſeÿ dann ſelber <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertig</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l11">Aber wir vvöllen das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen tün vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l10">auch </ab></add> die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l12">gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die Hercʒogen darynne <expan>anſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l13">Sun cʒü <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> empfahen wenn er <expan>hieʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l14">ſant Jacobs tag ſelber cʒü vns her gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kümt / vnd vor vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l15">tüt / als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat recht ıſt / . vvan wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l16">den vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen lıeb vnd frewntſchaft <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l17"><expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="64r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Gabriel Ridler, <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü München </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Ridler, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Anthoni
                            <expan>Ridl<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> suns,
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsts und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
                        Wilhalms, briefs ein abschrift und auch iren betbrief an uns damit gesant
                        habt, das alles <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. Nu ist <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        stat gewonheit nicht, daz wir yemanden czü <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>bey uns</add> empfahen <add>oder purkrecht versprechen</add>, er sey
                        dann selber <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertig</expan>. Aber wir wöllen das
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        willen tün und <add>auch</add> die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> unser
                        gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, die herczogen, darynne
                                <expan>anseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sun czü <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        empfahen, wenn er <expan>hiezwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sant Jacobs tag</q>25.07.1410</note></app> selber czü uns her gen
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kümt und vor uns tüt, als
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat recht ist. Wan wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit in den und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen lieb und frewntschaft
                                <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
